        "start": 610.52,
        "end": 611.88,
        "text": "“You got three priors, mate,",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 250,
        "start": 611.88,
        "end": 614.68,
        "text": "and that Monaro’s stolen, so tell it to the judge, buddy.”",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 251,
        "start": 614.68,
        "end": 616.56,
        "text": "So they put the wolf in jail.",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 252,
        "start": 616.56,
        "end": 618.56,
        "text": "Then the other pig, Gruey,",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 253,
        "start": 618.56,
        "end": 620.64,
        "text": "came and helped rebuild Jingo's house.",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 254,
        "start": 620.64,
        "end": 623.8,
        "text": "but this time, she used Besser blocks. - Dad, wait!",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 255,
        "start": 623.8,
        "end": 625.28,
        "text": "- Ah, yep. - (WHISPERS)",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 256,
        "start": 625.68,
        "end": 628.32,
        "text": "And they built a rad pool shaped like an ice cream cone",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 257,
        "start": 628.32,
        "end": 631.4,
        "text": "and filled it with lemonade. Wow. Good idea.",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 258,
        "start": 631.4,
        "end": 634.2,
        "text": "Meanwhile, the Big Bad Wolf scored a softy judge",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 259,
        "start": 634.2,
        "end": 635.88,
        "text": "and was out of jail on good behaviour.",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 260,
        "start": 636.2,
        "end": 638.96,
        "text": "But the judge said, “You gotta go say sorry to those pigs,",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 261,
        "start": 638.96,
        "end": 640.52,
        "text": "or you're back in here, buddy.”",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 262,
        "start": 640.52,
        "end": 642.64,
        "text": "So the wolf walked round to Jingo’s new joint",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 263,
        "start": 642.64,
        "end": 645.0,
        "text": "and Jingo and Gruey said, “Yeah, mate, it’s all cool.",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 264,
        "start": 645.0,
        "end": 646.24,
        "text": "Just don't try and eat us.”",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 265,
        "start": 646.24,
        "end": 647.0,
        "text": "And the wolf's like,",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 266,
        "start": 647.0,
        "end": 650.08,
        "text": "“Yeah, fair enough. I'm going vegan anyway. I just did tofu.”",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 267,
        "start": 650.08,
        "end": 652.8,
        "text": "So they invited him in for a swim to try and make friends,",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 268,
        "start": 652.8,
        "end": 655.8,
        "text": "but he kept peeing in the pool! [Together] Eeuuww!",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 269,
        "start": 656.2,
        "end": 658.8,
        "text": "So the pigs were like, “Stop peeing in our pool, mate!",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 270,
        "start": 658.8,
        "end": 660.6,
        "text": "It’s lemonade and we're trying to drink it!”",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 271,
        "start": 660.6,
        "end": 662.48,
        "text": "But really, even if it wasn't lemonade,",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 272,
        "start": 662.48,
        "end": 663.52,
        "text": "you shouldn't do it anyway.",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 273,
        "start": 663.52,
        "end": 664.52,
        "text": "It's full of nitrates",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 274,
        "start": 664.52,
        "end": 666.84,
        "text": "and now we're going to have to put heaps of algicide in.",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 275,
        "start": 666.84,
        "end": 668.68,
        "text": "But the Big Bad Wolf kept saying,",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 276,
        "start": 668.68,
        "end": 670.24,
        "text": "“Look, I didn’t pee in the pool!”",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 277,
        "start": 670.24,
        "end": 670.96,
        "text": "And the pigs are like,",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 278,
        "start": 670.96,
        "end": 672.2,
        "text": "“Yeah, you did,” and he’s like,",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 279,
        "start": 672.2,
        "end": 673.88,
        "text": "“Nah-ah, I don't do that sort of thing.",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 280,
        "start": 673.88,
        "end": 675.08,
        "text": "It's against my religion.”",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 281,
        "start": 675.08,
        "end": 677.64,
        "text": "So the next day, they put the stuff in the pool",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 282,
        "start": 677.64,
        "end": 680.12,
        "text": "that makes lemonade turn purple if you pee in it.",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 283,
        "start": 680.12,
        "end": 681.88,
        "text": "They didn't tell this to the Big Bad Wolf.",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 284,
        "start": 681.88,
        "end": 684.28,
        "text": "And he’s there swimming, eating some couscous,",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 285,
        "start": 684.28,
        "end": 685.56,
        "text": "talking about the Broncos.",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 286,
        "start": 685.56,
        "end": 688.16,
        "text": "Then he goes all quiet and stares into space for a second",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 287,
        "start": 688.16,
        "end": 689.92,
        "text": "with this sort of faraway look in his eyes.",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 288,
        "start": 689.92,
        "end": 691.68,
        "text": "And the kids are like, “Here we go... ”",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 289,
        "start": 691.68,
        "end": 694.16,
        "text": "And suddenly the lemonade turns purple around him",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 290,
        "start": 694.16,
        "end": 694.92,
        "text": "and the pigs are like,",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 291,
        "start": 694.92,
        "end": 697.24,
        "text": "“Ah, see! You’re a grub!”",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 292,
        "start": 697.24,
        "end": 699.56,
        "text": "So the wolf was really embarrassed and he ran out crying",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 293,
        "start": 699.56,
        "end": 700.56,
        "text": "and they never saw him again.",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 294,
        "start": 700.56,
        "end": 701.84,
        "text": "But apparently, he went on to become",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 295,
        "start": 701.84,
        "end": 703.32,
        "text": "quite a successful tennis player.",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 296,
        "start": 703.32,
        "end": 704.6,
        "text": "So, you know, the system works.",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 297,
        "start": 704.6,
        "end": 705.56,
        "text": "The end.",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 298,
        "start": 705.56,
        "end": 707.08,
        "text": "[Together] Again!  - No.",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 299,
        "start": 707.16,
        "end": 709.52,
        "text": "[Music] BLUEY THEME TUNE",
        "emoji": "💬"
    },
    {
        "id": 300,
        "start": 712.16,
        "end": 714.8,
        "text": "One day, there was a lovely big field",
        "emoji": "💬"
